# Source file for the auto-update pipeline's Python dependencies.
# Edit this file (NOT requirements.txt) to bump or add deps, then re-lock:
#
#     pip install pip-tools          # one-time
#     pip-compile scripts/requirements.in -o scripts/requirements.txt
#
# requirements.txt is the fully-resolved lockfile (including transitive
# deps) that the GitHub Action installs from. Pinning the full tree
# protects against supply-chain attacks via floor-constraint drift.

